enhanced_by.reason: Both methods involve operations related to small liability exchanges, making the setup for testing smallLiabilityExchangeHistory more comprehensive.
smallLiabilityAssets provides the list of assets suitable for small liability exchanges, which can be used to set up the test environment for smallLiabilityExchangeHistory.
transferHistory returns transfer history data, which can be used to verify the correctness of the small liability exchange history returned by smallLiabilityExchangeHistory.
repayRecord returns repayment records, which can be used to cross-verify the small liability exchange history for accuracy.
